name: Pet Plus
tag_list: pet, pets, pet-services, pet-medications, dog, dogs, dog-food, dog-toys, cat-food, cat-toys, dog-parks, grooming, petsitter
overview:
Pet Plus (Pet+) is an iPhone and iPad application that helps pet owners find pricing information for pet medications, find pet services information, and book pet-sitters.

Pet+ application features include: price comparison, which can help users see prices for medications; pet services, which can help users find local groomers, pet hotels, pet parks, and more; pet sitting, which can help users find pet-sitters; pets, where users can browse and share pet pictures; and lucky draw, which is a place where users can enter drawings to win pet goods as prizes.

The parent company of Pet Plus is Goumin.com, China’s largest online social network for pet owners.
